          "line_ref": "L29"
        },
        {
          "quote": "Interferon-associated antigen processing and presentation pathways increase.",
          "line_ref": "L43"
        }
      ],
      "caveat": "Immunopeptidomics measurements were strongest in specific model systems rather than uniformly across all tested settings."
