          "quote": "PD-L1 pathway activity also increases, creating a rationale for combining with checkpoint blockade.",
          "line_ref": "L45"
        }
      ],
      "caveat": "PD-L1 upregulation was observed in mouse models and may not translate equivalently to all human tumor types."
